{"id": "1435677743072411810", "channel_id": "1435677743072411810", "type": 0, "author_id": "452731110556696596", "author_name": "aurora3981", "author_bot": false, "content": "UID: 100804972\n\nGuide on how to get the highest PPS for the 200 posse event.\nThe idea is to regen 2k skey every turn via end turn button. \nI chose the shield posse instead of gate posse which regens 200 skey because gate posse is slow (requires selecting another posse) and only counts as one posse.\nHere's a checklist of things you need\n- arc2 rule set (d zone low alert) \n- pure chaos realm for keyflare <:realm_chaos:1437283650809888768> \n- awakers with keyflare stat built in\n- dust and dawn wheel\n- life drain covenant \n- thais wheel\n- covenant with keyflare substat\n- the best keyflare wheels you have\n- don't exalt / play card, just posse and end turn\n\n# Warning\nAt turn 99, enemy will use The End and kill you instantly thus not counting your posse uses. So avoid turn 99.", "timestamp": "2025-11-05T17:10:47.551000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-18T02:15:25.092000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "A_pinch", "emoji_id": "1432980538536493057", "count": 14}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}, {"emoji": "blowkiss", "emoji_id": "1356053035780014150", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "M_satisfy", "emoji_id": "1400771690321154110", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1435677743378333907", "filename": "Screenshot_20251106_005857_Gallery.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 88394, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1435677743072411810/1435677743378333907/Screenshot_20251106_005857_Gallery.jpg?ex=69cca8d7&is=69cb5757&hm=9e192970d894118885d02211969671403628ed2a8b81ebf18fbb638bda9fd97e&"}, {"id": "1435677744297152715", "filename": "Screenshot_20251106_005407_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 148546, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1435677743072411810/1435677744297152715/Screenshot_20251106_005407_Mo